Package: spatialCooccur
Type: Package
Title: Neighborhood Co-Occurrence and Spatial Interaction Analysis for Spatial Transcriptomics
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jun Inamo <jun.inamo@cuanschutz.edu> [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Jun Inamo <jun.inamo@cuanschutz.edu>
Description: This package provides a set of tools for analyzing neighborhood co-occurrence and spatial interactions in spatial transcriptomics data using Seurat objects. It includes spatial permutation tests, enrichment score calculations, and local diffusion modeling to evaluate cell-cell spatial relationships.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Depends: R (>= 4.1)
